text: Nicholas William Hamilton (born May 4, 2000) is an Australian actor and musician. He is known for his roles as Henry Bowers in It Chapter One and Chapter Two and superhero Maverick in Gen V. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:Australian movie actors Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:People from Lismore, New South Wales Category:Australian television actors Category:Musicians from New South Wales Category:Australian child actors Category:Actors from New South Wales
